description: I have a feeble for football. Or soccer as you guys say in the USA. I often walk in front of a stadium before a match and I love to watch the young fans. Well, I am always a bit shy about approaching them. Because you never know whether you talk to a hooligan. But this time I saw a guy coming alone. He was not so beautiful but looked very masculine. Well, I really didn´t expect him to be a student of Theology. Tough shit. Next try. Another boy was waiting for his friends. Obviously they flaked on him. So I offered him money if he shows me his body right away. And... he agreed. No discussion, nothing. He led me to his training place where he had the keys. And i had a lot of fun in the shower room.
title: Czech Hunter 26
